{"tid":1838761,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"135名武漢旅客抵菲律賓　菲國官員：會把他們送回去","createTime":"2020-01-24T06:42:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-25T08:03:42.000Z","uid":149494,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"e413f8f17fc118a0a66f4122358456cfcd8abb3d","tid":1838761,"uid":149494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T06:42:45.000Z","msg":"武漢肺炎蔓延之際，菲律賓宣布無限期停飛武漢往返班機，但已有135名來自武漢的旅客昨（23）日抵達菲律賓。菲國民航官員今天說，會用4班飛機把他們送回去。<br />\n<br />\nABS-CBN新聞網報導，菲律賓昨天宣布停飛往返武漢班機，但這135名旅客在此之前已抵達卡利波（Kalibo）國際機場。<br />\n<br />\n菲律賓民航委員會（CAB）法律部門主管薩莫迪歐（Wyrlou Samodio）表示，菲律賓皇家航空和菲律賓泛太平洋航空將用4班飛機把這些旅客送回武漢。<br />\n<br />\n卡利波機場是進出菲國觀光勝地長灘島（Boracay）主要門戶，而中國是菲律賓第2大旅客來源國，去年1到10月，有149萬9524人次中國旅客造訪菲律賓；2018年有125萬5258人次中國旅客抵菲。<br />\n<br />\n薩莫迪歐接受DZMM電台訪問時說：「他們必須回去，因為他們在這裡只是觀光客。」<br />\n<br />\n他並未說明這135名旅客回中國的航班時間。<br />\n<br />\n菲律賓每日詢問報（Philippine Daily Inquirer）報導，菲律賓衛生部次長杜明戈（Eric Domingo）說，今天起，中國抵菲航班旅客都會被要求填寫健康申報表，旅客必須揭露曾造訪地點、健康狀況等個人資訊。<br />\n<br />\n菲律賓民航委員會執行長阿西亞（Carmelo Arcilla）說，他們已下令航空公司依循標準作業程序監控可能感染2019新型冠狀病毒（2019-nCoV）的旅客，空服員也被要求密切觀察出現病徵的旅客。<br />\n<br />\n菲律賓交通部長杜加德（Arthur Tugade）要求相關部門因應農曆春節預計將湧入菲國的旅客，採取一切必要措施防堵新型冠狀病毒擴散。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.setn.com/m/news.aspx?newsid=678233\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.setn.com%2Fm%2Fnews.aspx%3Fnewsid%3D678233&d=J5HXnbFloTEqGlUzWM3JXw2CFyCB1h158poew6f0R2E%3D&h=6d3dd157\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.setn.com%2Fm%2Fnews.aspx%3Fnewsid%3D678233&h=c9d8d458\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.setn.com/m/news.aspx?newsid=678233</a>"},{"pid":"dfe0dc7447ea0b323165b83749899d9a93bbf4e3","tid":1838761,"uid":253978,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T06:43:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44b33530aeaf15ace5def7d6f89d15e6af43f6bb","tid":1838761,"uid":32204,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T06:44:01.000Z","msg":"班友仲出去害人<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7e77230b9c1c3eb7baa55cefe05a52cb2b1d326","tid":1838761,"uid":37661,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T06:44:29.000Z","msg":"直接送佢哋返舊時嗰度啦。"},{"pid":"1e6bb1d53117af0e934f24125785800549148e8e","tid":1838761,"uid":27432,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T06:45:46.000Z","msg":"相反香港<br />\n<br />\nWelcome welcome 相當吸引<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5d5862eb0aedb9b71919ab8241ea2110dd7eaef","tid":1838761,"uid":149494,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"1e6bb1d53117af0e934f24125785800549148e8e","tid":1838761,"uid":27432,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T06:45:46.000Z","msg":"相反香港<br />\n<br />\nWelcome welcome 相當吸引<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T06:57:43.000Z","msg":"屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"842048a254ae6fed48557caa169cb7f94337616a","tid":1838761,"uid":339539,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T06:57:51.000Z","msg":"賓仔真係做野"},{"pid":"c53a75a22b406ecb7dd0b1a24dc1d675fb9f41bf","tid":1838761,"uid":92353,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T07:01:31.000Z","msg":"有主權先有say<br />\n冇主權就任人魚肉"},{"pid":"29bbc919ada4f30100dfa645fee077d9f47e03c3","tid":1838761,"uid":257914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T11:23:29.000Z","msg":"香港 = 第三世界<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9227560af8bf4f6942bda9554713b9c6118e0f31","tid":1838761,"uid":260788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T08:03:42.000Z","msg":"W"}]}